Package: com.android.build.gradle.internal.variant

[Java] Class ApplicationVariantFactory

    • com.android.build.gradle.internal.variant.ApplicationVariantFactory
    • All Implemented Interfaces and Traits:
      VariantFactory

      public class ApplicationVariantFactory
extends Object

      An implementation of VariantFactory for a project that generates APKs. This can be an app project, or a test-only project, though the default behavior is app.
